<font color="#ffff00"><b>-You're so sweet.
-Okay.</b></font>

43
00:04:08,175 --> 00:04:09,575
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How long have you been in Shanghai?</b></font>

44
00:04:10,255 --> 00:04:11,335
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I just arrived here.</b></font>

45
00:04:11,655 --> 00:04:12,775
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Really?</b></font>

46
00:04:13,095 --> 00:04:14,935
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're the first person I know here.</b></font>

47
00:04:15,015 --> 00:04:17,095
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Let's toast to our encounter.
