55
00:04:44,295 --> 00:04:45,135
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right.</b></font>

56
00:04:45,695 --> 00:04:49,375
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think you like fruity cocktails.</b></font>

57
00:04:49,575 --> 00:04:50,575
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The sweet ones.</b></font>

58
00:04:51,215 --> 00:04:52,255
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

59
00:04:53,695 --> 00:04:55,895
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's okay. I'll order if I want something.</b></font>

60
00:04:56,335 --> 00:05:01,015
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aren't you here all alone
so that someone else can order for you?</b></font>

61
00:05:01,575 --> 00:05:03,415
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No, that's not why I'm here.</b></font>

62
00:05:04,975 --> 00:05:07,535
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I noticed you immediately
when you came in.</b></font>

63
00:05:08,095 --> 00:05:09,855
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You sat here and didn't order anything.</b></font>

64
00:05:10,495 --> 00:05:13,935
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Weren't you hoping someone
