66
00:05:17,815 --> 00:05:19,855
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't know the rules
since it's my first time here.</b></font>

67
00:05:23,135 --> 00:05:24,575
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're such a cute girl.</b></font>

68
00:05:24,655 --> 00:05:26,375
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No problem. Let's drink.</b></font>

69
