<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's my treat. Order whatever you want.</b></font>

70
00:05:37,135 --> 00:05:38,295
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay. Let's drink.</b></font>

71
00:05:39,375 --> 00:05:42,455
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I can tell that you're not a girl
