<font color="#ffff00"><b>Someone bought me a drink
when it's my first time here.</b></font>

76
00:05:52,335 --> 00:05:53,495
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm quite lucky too.</b></font>

77
00:05:55,095 --> 00:05:56,455
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How alcohol tolerant are you?</b></font>

78
00:05:58,375 --> 00:05:59,975
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I haven't really drunk that much before.</b></font>

79
00:06:00,055 --> 00:06:02,975
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then you will know
how much you can drink today.</b></font>

80
00:06:08,415 --> 00:06:09,255
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ximen.</b></font>

81
00:06:11,135 --> 00:06:12,655
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where are we going later?</b></font>

82
00:06:13,215 --> 00:06:16,255
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Karaoke? A restaurant? Or to your place?</b></font>

83
00:06:16,535 --> 00:06:18,975
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-To your place, of course.
-Really?</b></font>

84
00:06:19,735 --> 00:06:21,535
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Xiaoyou is drinking too much.
