98
00:07:09,575 --> 00:07:11,295
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't want to owe you anything.</b></font>

99
00:07:13,255 --> 00:07:15,215
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We'll have the same again.</b></font>

100
00:07:15,775 --> 00:07:18,295
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Are you drunk?
-I'm not.</b></font>

101
00:07:18,375 --> 00:07:20,415
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-My face is just a bit hot.
